<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.6">
<l>aṅkam viṭṭavai yaintuma kaṟṟi</l>
<l rend="indent">yāvi mūkkiṉil cōtitta piṉṉai</l>
<l>caṅkam viṭṭavar kaiyaima ṟittup</l>
<l rend="indent">paiya vētalai cāyppataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>vaṅkam viṭṭula vumkaṭaṟ paḷḷi</l>
<l rend="indent">māya ṉaimatu cūtaṉaṉai mārpil</l>
<l>taṅka viṭṭuvait tāvatōr karumam</l>
<l rend="indent">cātip pārkkeṉṟum cātikka lāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who adhere to one act,</l>
<l>placing and firmly establishing in [their] hearts</l>
<l>Matucūtaṉaṉ, Māyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose bed is in the sea where ships roam,</l>
<l>before the five senses, expelled, abandon the body,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] after testing the nose for breath,</l>
<l rend="indent">the assembly leaves,</l>
<l rend="indent">waving their hands and</l>
<l rend="indent">lowly lowering [their] heads,</l>
<l>[they] will persist forever.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
